ENG: In 1957, Simon proposed the notion of Bounded Rationality as the property of an agent that behaves in a manner that is nearly optimal with respect to its goals as its resources will allow.
ANU: 1957 meM, simona ne eka prawiniXi ke guNa ke jEsA bAvndada rESanElitI kI XAraNA praswAva raKI jo eka Ese AcaraNa meM vyavahAra karawA hE jo usakA lakRya sanxarBa karIba karIba sarvowkqRta howA hE jEsA ki usakA saMsAXana anumawi xeMge .
